import { Component, HostListener } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { LayoutService } from 'src/app/layout/service/app.layout.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-landing', templateUrl: './landing.component.html' }) export class LandingComponent { isNavbarGray = false; constructor(public layoutService: LayoutService, public router: Router) { } @HostListener('window:scroll', []) onWindowScroll() { // Add a scroll event listener to toggle the class based on the scroll position this.isNavbarGray = window.scrollY > 100; // Adjust the scroll position threshold } }
